Localizar archivos JavaScript
# Con subfinder + httpx + waybackurls
subfinder -d target.com | httpx -mc 200 | waybackurls | grep "\.js" | sort -u > js_files.txt

O con gau:

gau target.com | grep "\.js" | sort -u > js_files.txtgrep "\.js" | sort -u > js_files.txt

Descargar los archivos

cat js_files.txt | while read url; do
  wget $url -P js_downloads/
done

Analizar los JS
 Buscar endpoints y rutas internas
grep -Eo "(https?:\/\/[a-zA-Z0-9\.\/\-\_]+)" js_downloads/*.js | sort -u

3.2 Buscar secretos y claves API
grep -Ei "api_key|apikey|secret|token|password|auth" js_downloads/*.js


Usar herramientas especializadas
SecretFinder
python3 SecretFinder.py -i js_files.txt -o results.html.py -i js_files.txt -o results.html

LinkFinder (para endpoints)
python3 linkfinder.py -i js_files.txt -o cli.py -i js_files.txt -o cli
